TableDefinition.DatabaseQuery: SELECT c.dn, c.attribute_1, c.attribute_2, c.attribute_3, c.attribute_4, c.attribute_5, c.attribute_6, c.attribute_7, c.attribute_8, c.attribute_9 FROM Cache_table_ad c INNER JOIN ObjectAttributes oa_key ON c.dn = oa_key.attribute_value AND oa_key.id_attribute = (SELECT id FROM Attributes WHERE is_key = 1 AND name = 'distinguishedName') INNER JOIN Objects o ON o.id = oa_key.id_object AND o.id_snapshot = (SELECT MAX(id) FROM Snapshots) INNER JOIN ObjectAttributes oa_show ON oa_show.id_object = o.id AND oa_show.id_attribute = (SELECT id FROM Attributes WHERE name = 'displayName') WHERE oa_show.attribute_value LIKE '%%HR_e_naam%%'
